# Directory structure of Axionyx_KG

* Main: Contains ax_main.cpp and main.cpp (the main program loops) and AxBld.cpp, the LevelBld derived class that tells Axionyx_KG which implementation to deploy. *Add your ifdef here to select the physics you want to run!*
* Base: Contains the abstract base classes
* Impl: Contains the implementations of the abstract base classes
* Gravity: Contains the gravity-specific code
* Particle: Contains the particle-specific code
* Utils: Contains helper functions for various parts of the code
* IO: Contains input/output-related code
* Timestep: Contains the code related to advancing fields and particles in time
